qmt library installation

1) unpack qmt-xxx.tar.gz.

2) In the directory where the qmt distribution is unpacked, run configure 
script.

3) Different barrier algorithms can be used: queue-based (default), 
centralized and lock based. These options can be enabled by configure 
--enable-xxx.

4) If public APIs are desired, configure --enable-public-release.

5) Run quick test by make check.

6) Make sure compile library on the machine you are going to run your code.
The AMD and Intel machines have subtle differences.


